- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper deals with the representation of numbers in a generalized system. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper investigates the syntactical properties of words in a regular language. 
- cs.NT (Number Theory) is relevant as the paper discusses the representation of real numbers and their properties.
